         <div xml:id="alalal-e20909"><!-- l3d5a6 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-e20909-Hd1e99">Articulus 6</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-e20909-Hd1e101" type="question-title">Utrum tota Trinitas sit operata 
susceptionem humane nature ?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e20909-d1e104">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="30"/>ARTICULUS VI.
<lb ed="Bd" n="31"/>Utrum tota Trinitas sit operata 
suscep<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="32"/>tionem humane nature ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e20909-d1e113">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="33"/>Deinde quaeritur de hoc quod dicit,
<lb ed="Bd" n="34"/>ibi, A, 82: <quote xml:id="alalal-e20909-Qd1e119"> Cum tota Lrinitas operata
<lb ed="Bd" n="35"/>sit formationem suscepti hominis, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e20909-d1e125">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="36"/>Hoc infra negabit magister.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e20909-d1e131">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="37"/>Solutio Dicendum secundum 
com<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="38"/>muniter glossantes hujus verbi, suscepti
<cb ed="#Bd" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="39"/>hominis, id est, humane nature. Vel
<lb ed="Bd" n="40"/>potest dici secundum preedicta, quod 
li<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="41"/>cet homo non susceptus sit, tamen id
<lb ed="Bd" n="42"/>quod suscipitur, consequitur esse 
homi<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="43"/>nis eo quod suscipiendo unit corpus et
<lb ed="Bd" n="44"/>animam et format et perficit : et ita licet
<lb ed="Bd" n="45"/>non primo, tamen consequenter homo
<lb ed="Bd" n="46"/>per susceptionem habetur a Filio Dei, et
<lb ed="Bd" n="47"/>ipse est ille homo, eo quod unio facta
<lb ed="Bd" n="48"/>estin hypostasi.
</p>
         </div>
